<h2 i18n:translate="">About eduCommons</h2>

<p i18n:translate="">eduCommons' goals are to:</p>

<ul>
  <li i18n:translate=""> Provide free, searchable, access to course materials for educators, 
       students, and self-learners around the world.</li>
  <li i18n:translate=""> Catalyze the growth of communities of learners.</li>
  <li i18n:translate=""> Extend the reach and impact of the OpenCourseWare concept.</li>
</ul>

